<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Thank you for the cross, Lord</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Worthy is the Lamb

[V2]
 Thank you for the cross, Lord
 Thank you for the price you paid
 Bearing all my sin and shame,
 In love you came
 And gave amazing grace.

[C1]
   Thank you for your love, Lord.
   Thank you for your nail-pierced hands.
   Washed me in your cleansing flow,
   Now all I know -
   Your forgiveness and embrace!

[V3]
 Worthy is the Lamb,
 Seated on the throne
 Crown you now with many crowns,
 You reign forevermore!
 High and lifted up,
 Jesus Son of God,
 The Darling of Heaven crucified
 Worthy is the Lamb!
 Worthy is the Lamb!

[V4]
 madloba jvartsmistvis
 sheni tsʼminda siskhlistvis
 chemi gamosqʼidvistvis,
 im pasistvis
 romlitats mikhseni

[C2]
   madloba upalo
   shen chʼrilobebistvis
   sheni siqʼvarulistvis
   pʼatʼiebistvis
   romelits dzalas madzlevs

[V5]
 ghirsia kʼravi
 taqʼvanistsemis
 man ise shegiqʼvara, rom
 jvarze mokʼvda is chemtvis
 agamaghleb shen,
